{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
        (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
          Diagonalizable := ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n 𝕜), P⁻¹ * A * P = D ∧ D.IsDiagonal

{n : Type u} →
  {𝕜 : Type v} →
  [inst : Field 𝕜] →
  [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
  [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
  (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), (Invertible P) ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsDiagonal D ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

{n : Type u_1} {𝕜 : Type u_2} [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : Fintype n] [inst_2 : DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (⅟P * A * P)

{n : Type u_1} →
  (A : Matrix n n ℂ) →
    ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ) [inst : Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (⅟P * A * P)

{n : Type u} → 
  {𝕜 : Type v} → 
    [inst : Field 𝕜] → 
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] → 
        [inst_2 : DecidableEq n] → 
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) → 
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [Invertible P], P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = Matrix.diagonal (Matrix.eigenvalues A)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {α : Type u_3} →
    [inst : Fintype n] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Field α] →
          (A : Matrix n n α) →
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), Invertible P ∧ Matrix.IsDiag (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_1} (A : Matrix n n ℂ) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ) [Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (⅟P * A * P)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_3} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
          Prop :=
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsUnit P ∧ IsDiag (P⁻¹ * A * P)
